title: TDP-9 | Community Member of the Week | 2021-W41 | Blursday
body:
# Overview
Community Member of the Week (nomination / reward program) rewards 100 $RETOKEN.  Special exceptions can be made to expand this (IE: multiple people, etc).  This is a fun way that we recognize those that are building this community.

# 2021-W41 | Nominations
@Blursday was nominated by @AmyMarcella during Core Team | 2021-W42 | Weekly Planning Session on 17Oct2021.  @Yonks 2nd'ed this nomination.
